{"tid":165454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作死不離三兄弟","createTime":"2017-03-21T11:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T22:35:32.000Z","uid":9924,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"075c2e8a63f1efa552440f4d5f72d9e79802428f","tid":165454,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CMvBq7RXV8s?t=35m53s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCMvBq7RXV8s%3Ft%3D35m53s&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm9%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=aa08a301\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CMvBq7RXV8s?t=35m53s</a><br />\n岩岩先睇返<br />\n原來作死不離三兄弟係個陣都有講過學生自殺既問題<br />\n都覺得講得幾岩<br />\n學生陷入瘋狂既競賽中<br />\n得到既唔係知識而係壓力<br />\n學校變成一個壓力鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9ad3c3bafe823756dcaba4b186cc26b19269d0","tid":165454,"uid":8733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"呢套又好笑 又有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2be48cc33a8141952d30fd6029ff5cf9e1a8e0","tid":165454,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"真係神戲，睇過幾次，香港上映果時都有入戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a57ee8f3210cbf869f497390538810f023ba238","tid":165454,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係神戲，睇過幾次，香港上映果時都有入戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個當笑片咁睇<br />\n而家睇返真係都幾貼近我地生活<br />\n我CAP既前小小就係個學生比個PROFESSOR BAN左佢份功課<br />\n仲要打埋電話同佢老豆講佢畢唔到業<br />\n搞到個學生走頭無路去自殺<br />\n主角攞左佢部直昇機調整之後變左航拍機出黎 個陣應該一D都唔興呢樣掛<br />\n最諷刺就係主角用佢部機黎發現個學生自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f35e4fb42992a2657949da73406659ca95269d0","tid":165454,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:23:55.000Z","msg":"發現新大陸"},{"pid":"8d4576aec918ae1014e85c5860fcf696dd9856ea","tid":165454,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發現新大陸</blockquote><br />\n溫故知新唔同發現新大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f4c1aad8ed531df05800d757fc6a7dbf2dad40","tid":165454,"uid":82500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係神戲，睇過幾次，香港上映果時都有入戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個當笑片咁睇<br />\n而家睇返真係都幾貼近我地生活<br />\n我CAP既前小小就係個學生比個PROFESSOR BAN左佢份功課<br />\n仲要打埋電話同佢老豆講佢畢唔到業<br />\n搞到個學生走頭無路去自殺<br />\n主角攞左佢部直昇機調整之後變左航拍機出黎 個陣應該一D都唔興呢樣掛<br />\n最諷刺就係主角用佢部機黎發現個學生自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次睇呢幕，好傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb714fd5fe09b270b8f0d3f9936d41e7d310fe80","tid":165454,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:33:22.000Z","msg":"呢套我都有睇<br />\n真係好正"},{"pid":"85a69a68ef2591932823b415584d3dd04a5c6d9c","tid":165454,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"睇左幾次，神作中的神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbb96bce73b143f59c9299b51e879959eb80793","tid":165454,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"睇咗好多次，仲要明明網上都有得睇，睇到識背咁滯，都入戲院支持，再笑同喊多次。<br />\n<br />\n呢套戲真係兜巴打落班話有 BT 冇人會入戲院睇戲嘅電影工作者！<br />\n<br />\n香港做咗四個月，收二千幾萬。"},{"pid":"25ea1fc9a0125e710cb387732fd887f60b8bc46d","tid":165454,"uid":76801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"我早兩日都又睇左次 真係好好睇 雖然都重係接受唔到啲印度片成日冇啦啦跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d86e716b41f7ce172506af187d6deea87bda5df","tid":165454,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"經典只所以係經典<br />\n係因為它有一種百看不厭的魅力"},{"pid":"66ecaf091584279dc11cf9979b03fda2806f08c3","tid":165454,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n套戲改變左我諗野既方法"},{"pid":"d0dd007fc7efe65ebc4c9f52b6ace428d7b683a3","tid":165454,"uid":3567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我早兩日都又睇左次 真係好好睇 雖然都重係接受唔到啲印度片成日冇啦啦跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歌舞係一定有嘅元素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e6126f362f027d464d1608725355da22d05b07","tid":165454,"uid":29549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩先睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce788953f329d04539b702d074ccd58c42a85de","tid":165454,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:26:28.000Z","msg":"play store 得書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無地方可以睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bfb39c899d5559af3f8c4ab439e4b18679c536","tid":165454,"uid":82500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>play store 得書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無地方可以睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主咪有link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dffee70ce4561587fb472968cd7dec93bff9a9","tid":165454,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我早兩日都又睇左次 真係好好睇 雖然都重係接受唔到啲印度片成日冇啦啦跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歌舞係一定有嘅元素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd印度鄉村窮鬼好度縮，覺得睇戲要睇得耐先夠皮，所以片商唯有加多d歌舞元素拖時間，比佢地消磨半日時間"},{"pid":"4d226ef5492299c5b5b986cd3cf081e9fc9f7208","tid":165454,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>play store 得書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無地方可以睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主咪有link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒左，係街無click入去以為preview<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82ce49f814ba03cdaad1dc24c161dc65790e5be","tid":165454,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係神戲，睇過幾次，香港上映果時都有入戲院睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個當笑片咁睇<br />\n而家睇返真係都幾貼近我地生活<br />\n我CAP既前小小就係個學生比個PROFESSOR BAN左佢份功課<br />\n仲要打埋電話同佢老豆講佢畢唔到業<br />\n搞到個學生走頭無路去自殺<br />\n主角攞左佢部直昇機調整之後變左航拍機出黎 個陣應該一D都唔興呢樣掛<br />\n最諷刺就係主角用佢部機黎發現個學生自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有幾場戲都好深刻<br />\n例如最初有個老師問主角咩係機械, 個主角用佢既字眼解釋一次, 但個老師就一定要跟書本上定義先係正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地讀書果時咪就係咁, 一味抄書, 考試就夾硬背個答案出黎, 根本唔會有自己想法"},{"pid":"ea2bff5d652787a555ca170203fa0486526baa85","tid":165454,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"買了DVD準